description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 75, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 225, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 8 for East, 8 for South, and 3 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [225 Votes, Top 5% Score]
